    <h1>Google Sandbox</h1>
    <p class="description">An unconfirmed theory that <strong>new websites face a 3-6 month probationary period</strong> where rankings are suppressed — even with quality content and backlinks. Only 5.7% of new pages reach the top 10 within one year.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
